title: 1989 Licence to Kill - Movie Sequence Soundtrack
description:
Licence to Kill (1989) Movie Sequence Soundtrack

mp3 Bitrate 128


This is a reedited edition of the soundtrack album. The original tracks 

have been sequenced the way they occur in the movie. The suite is edited

and split up into ques and inserted where they actually belong. Unfortunately more 

music exists, but hasn't been released. At least not yet. Therefore this is the 

closest possible to a correctly sequenced soundtrack album I've been able to 

achieve.

I hope you'll like it.
